message.content:
Rule Learning, Probabilistic Methods. 

Rule Learning is present in the text as the paper presents a new algorithm called Structural Regression Trees (SRT) which constructs a tree containing a literal or a conjunction of literals in each node, and assigns a numerical value to each leaf. 

Probabilistic Methods are present in the text as the paper integrates the statistical method of regression trees into ILP to predict numerical values from examples and relational and mostly non-determinate background knowledge.
